<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Neorthostigma macrops (Stelfox &amp; Graham, 1951) (A, B female, holotype of A. macrops; C-F female, holotype of Neorthostigma eoum) A, C habitus, lateral view B habitus, dorsal view D head and mesosoma, lateral view E mandible F antenna." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.80.58737.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/490439" pageId="0" pageNumber="31">5A</figureCitation>
